      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JUNK YARD JEFF (1) had a tough draw to overcome and was game in defeat when only half a length from Junk Yard Hippy in third (17.38) at this track. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Deserves serious consideration. AEROPLANE PENNY (8) turned in a plain performance last time when sixth at this track over 300m behind Regency Boy (17.82) in a Grade 5/6. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and six minor placings to her credit. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. BENNY THE BULL (7) missed the frame last time but prior to that was an effortless Grade 6 winner (17.18) at this track, scoring by 3 lengths. Well placed here and should do much better. WILD MOOD (2) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
